		Our first target is a massive blue gel polymer.
		Blast it open from the inside.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_1:
		'''
		We need to eliminate that giant eye; it comes from a powerful organism.
		I need to dissect it to see how it achieves anti-gravity.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_2:
		'''
		Whether it is the giant worm coiling in the corruption,
