		Cut out their cores; I want to study this terrifying ecological invasiveness.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_3:
		'''
		Gel has actually derived a god?
		I feel it is just a filthy aggregation that swallowed too many impurities.
		Let us help it undergo a thorough purification separation
