		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_4:
		'''
		A wall of flesh spanning the Underworld; it is a seal of the old era.
		We need enough firepower to blast through this organic barrier.
		This will be our opening act for the new era.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_5:
		'''
		The giant worm of the Sulphurous Sea has surfaced.
		Remove its feeding organs; I need to understand how this contamination source works.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_6:
		'''
		The brimstone herald deep in the lava is spreading a high-heat reaction.
		Extinguish its core flame, and record its energy conversion efficiency while you are there.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_7:
		'''
		The first mechanical target is a giant steel worm.
		Cut it into recyclable scrap, and try to preserve the drive structure.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_8:
		'''
		The second mechanical target is that pair of mirrored airborne eyes.
		Dismantle their weapon modules one by one, and do not let the lasers ruin the samples.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_9:
		'''
		The final mechanical target wears the old king's skull.
		Shatter that metal head, and we can shut down this mechanical invasion protocol.
