		Go destroy that counterfeit.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_11:
		'''
		Deep in the Jungle, several flamboyant buds have bloomed.
		We need to investigate and collect experimental data.
		''' */
	/* TrialSummary_12:
		'''
		The ancient robot deep in the Temple awaits a recharge activation.
